rComments: He's really funny and approachable! He rambles in his lectures, but everything you need to know is in the textbook. This class is easy and interesting!

This class is difficult because he doesn't make the test the TA's do and they don't attend lecture. So whatever Denasi talks about is genrally not on the test.  It's just a really hard class to understand in terms of structure.  You must be a free spirit and not care at all about academics to enjoy it.
